<L>__{exterior hillside and gate pre dawn}
<A>__{a luminous procession passes through a moorish stone gate, down to the harbor. we see the faces of the sailors and their families columbus, pinzon amongst them we sense the fervor and apprehension of the departure. the procession is lead by marchena and four young novices carrying the madonna. all hold long, burning tapers, saying the rosary. a sailor pushes through the crowd, and kisses the madonna's feet.}
